    "course_title": "OBSTETRICS & GYNECOLOGY INPATIENT ACTING INTERNSHIP",
    "description": "Provides an in-depth exposure to inpatient and operative management of complicated obstetric and gynecologic patients. Work under the direct supervision of a senior resident, fellows and the obstetrician-gynecology faculty. Provides an opportunity to function at the intern level and play an active role in inpatient management of obstetric and gynecologic patients.",
